title: Semifinal breakdown: Dire Wolves vs Legacy

replies.body: I have to agree with minky on this one. By far

legacy is going to get too confident in the first couple of matches and give it to dire wolves. i reckon the third and possible forth match are the ones to watch. DW is focusing on their own weaknesses while Legacy is trying to play at there peak 100% of the time which is impossible. so instead of trying to make your highers higher they should make there lowers higher.
